Which KSP version are you running and what mods do you have?

I’ve never seen anything like that happening before, try reloading the game and see if it happens again.

If you have any graphics mods like EVE installed make sure they’re the right version for your version of KSP. If you recently added a mod/mods, try removing them and see if the problem persists. If that doesn’t fix the problem try updating your graphics driver software, and if that still doesn’t fix it find the Player.log file (on windows it’s in C:/users/your username/appdata/locallow/squad/kerbal space program) and upload that to a file share website then post a link to it here, it might say what the problem is.
